# multipleBox

### 一、组件说明
#### 1. 概述
多选框组件，当所有`options`都选中，`全部`也会被勾选，且与选项在同一行。

#### 2. 应用场景
用于一组可选项多项选择，或者单独用于标记切换某种状态。

### 二、使用说明
> 引用
```
import multipleBox from 'professionalComponents/multipleBox';
```

> 应用
```
<multipleBox
  :values="values"
  :options="options"
  @changeOptions="checkOrderTypeChange"
/>
```
```
export default {
  components: {
    multipleBox
  },
  data(){
    return {
      options: [
          {"title":"正常","value":"1"},
          {"title":"换货","value":"2"},
          {"title":"补发","value":"4"},
          {"title":"虚拟","value":"8"},
          {"title":"预售","value":"32"},
          {"title":"天猫","value":"602"}
      ],
      values: ["1","2","4","8","32","602"]
    }
  },
  methods: {
    checkOrderTypeChange(vals) {
        console.log(vals)
    }
  }
}
```

### 三、API

#### multipleBox Props

属性 | 说明 | 类型 | 默认值
